          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500; margin-top:2px !important">Rebalancing of the US-Europe relations</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/us-vice-president-jd-vance-speech-munich-security-conference.png" alt="U.S. Vice President JD Vance gives a speech at the Munich Security Conference in Munich, German" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
